data.description: Discover this charming 1,469 square foot home nestled on a peaceful street, set on a generous 5,227 square foot lot. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, it offers the perfect space for your family. The stunning landscaping enhances its curb appeal, inviting you in to explore. Step inside to find numerous updates throughout, including all-new flooring and modern kitchen countertops, creating an inviting and stylish interior. Meticulously maintained, this home radiates cleanliness and care. Don't miss the opportunity to see this gem firsthand. A must-see for any homebuyer seeking comfort and tranquility.
